# Environment Variables (Optional)
# This project runs entirely client-side and doesn't require any environment variables
# Add here if you need API keys for future features

# Example: Google Analytics (if you add analytics later)
# VITE_GA_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# Example: API endpoint (if you add backend later)
# VITE_API_URL=https://api.utilityhub.com

# Note: All VITE_ prefixed variables are exposed to the client
# Never put secrets here - this is a client-side app!
